---
title: 'Aim 3: Clinical Prediction'
---

### Develop novel clinical prediction methodologies 

To develop and evaluate algorithms for: 

  1. Automated feature selection and engineering
  2. Suicide risk prediction 
  3. Predicting heterogeneous treatment effects via causal modeling 
  4. Recalibrated risk estimates via semi-supervised learning
  5. Transfer learning and collaborative co-training strategies to enhance risk prediction to improve generalizability
